    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你正在试玩体验版。这只是未来精彩内容的一小部分！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024780/extras/0051c7fc16143f84bded6ba7d50316c4.poster.avif?t=1756645611\" width=614 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024780/extras/0051c7fc16143f84bded6ba7d50316c4.webm?t=1756645611\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024780/extras/0051c7fc16143f84bded6ba7d50316c4.mp4?t=1756645611\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t你继承了家族清洁生意，现在轮到你拿起吸尘器，继续完成使命。从温馨的住宅、混乱的艺术馆，到太空站和阳光海滩，踏上各种独特地点的清洁任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024780/extras/5885825600ceb7081a461a8eb805abbd.poster.avif?t=1756645611\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024780/extras/5885825600ceb7081a461a8eb805abbd.webm?t=1756645611\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024780/extras/5885825600ceb7081a461a8eb805abbd.mp4?t=1756645611\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t用海绵、吸尘器、蒸汽清洁器和全新的高压水枪清除污垢、洗净污渍、恢复秩序。完成任务赚取报酬，解锁更多工具，扩充你的清洁装备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024780/extras/839aaefa1d6c6c39b2389316111b73a1.poster.avif?t=1756645611\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024780/extras/839aaefa1d6c6c39b2389316111b73a1.webm?t=1756645611\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024780/extras/839aaefa1d6c6c39b2389316111b73a1.mp4?t=1756645611\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t通过不同的手套、垃圾桶等来自定义你的装备。无论你喜欢简约干净，还是色彩斑斓的混乱，都可以打造属于你的风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024780/extras/7abf996f9e970fc40dd3c8231cbbcb8f.poster.avif?t=1756645611\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024780/extras/7abf996f9e970fc40dd3c8231cbbcb8f.webm?t=1756645611\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024780/extras/7abf996f9e970fc40dd3c8231cbbcb8f.mp4?t=1756645611\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t不着急，不紧张——只有你、你的工具，还有等待你将其变为完美的混乱环境。按自己的节奏游戏，享受令人奇妙满足的清洁乐趣。想要挑战？试试高效完成任务，登上排行榜吧！</p>",
